J. Crew Group, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 12:22 AM ET
Specialty Retail

Company Overview of J. Crew Group, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
J.Crew Group, Inc. operates as a multi-brand apparel and accessories retailer in the United States, Canada, the United Kingdom, Hong Kong, and France. The company provides an assortment of women’s and men’s apparel and accessories, including outerwear, suiting, casual attire, swimwear, shoes, handbags, belts, socks, jewelry, and others, as well as casual T-shirts, denims, hand-embellished sweaters and coats, Italian cashmere, limited edition prints and patterns, and vintage inspired details under the J.Crew brand. It also offers a product assortment of apparel and accessories for the children’s market under the Crewcuts brand, as well as products for women comprising jeans, tees, ankle boots...
J.Crew Group, Inc. operates as a multi-brand apparel and accessories retailer in the United States, Canada, the United Kingdom, Hong Kong, and France. The company provides an assortment of women’s and men’s apparel and accessories, including outerwear, suiting, casual attire, swimwear, shoes, handbags, belts, socks, jewelry, and others, as well as casual T-shirts, denims, hand-embellished sweaters and coats, Italian cashmere, limited edition prints and patterns, and vintage inspired details under the J.Crew brand. It also offers a product assortment of apparel and accessories for the children’s market under the Crewcuts brand, as well as products for women comprising jeans, tees, ankle boots, and leather jackets under the Madewell brand. The company markets and sells its products through its retail and factory stores, Websites, and catalogs. As of June 12, 2017, it operated 278 J.Crew retail stores; 117 Madewell stores; 178 factory stores, including 39 J.Crew Mercantile stores; and Websites comprising jcrew.com, jcrewfactory.com, madewell.com, as well as the J.Crew catalog. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in New York, New York. J.Crew Group, Inc. is a subsidiary of Chinos Holdings, Inc.
Detailed Description


